column2: "value": "**Artist || Author || Metaphysician || Mystic**\r\n\r\n\u200b\u200b The oldest of thirteen siblings
column3: I was raised & homeschooled among the serene landscapes of Lancaster County
column4: PA (USA).\r\n\r\n\u200b\u200b\u200b Following two USMC combat tours in Iraq
column5: and a subsequent decade of contracting work
column6:
I turned to painting & writing in an effort to resolve my intensifying emotional & physical health issues.

​​​​ I now aim to share my gifts to increase the measure of calm & tranquility in the world.

**Artist**
